Package me.s3ns3iw00.jcommands.argument.autocomplete.type

Class SearchAutocomplete

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.s3ns3iw00.jcommands.argument.autocomplete.Autocomplete
      • me.s3ns3iw00.jcommands.argument.autocomplete.type.SearchAutocomplete
  • public class SearchAutocomplete
extends Autocomplete
    A type of Autocomplete that takes a datasource and returns a list of Choice based on user input, like a search bar The minimum number of characters for searching can be limited, the result can be sorted, its number can be limited

    NOTE: This is currently supports only String and Number type of datasource! The datasource's type has been determined by the SearchAutocomplete.SearchType, and any other type of value in the datasource is ignored!
